{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A robot action game where you can freely customize the battle mech &quot;VersionThree&quot; (V3). Players take on various missions as mercenaries piloting V3, eventually uncovering a global conspiracy...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Gamepad  is required, such as DualShock 4, DualSense, or Xbox. Additionally, keyboard is\u00a0 only used for entering text within the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Assembly</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The combat mech &quot;V3&quot; piloted by players can be customized to their liking by combining different parts. Different parts allow for different actions, and customizing your mech to suit the situation greatly affects the game's difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509800/extras/assen.gif?t=1737777016\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Missions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will accept &quot;missions&quot; from various factions as mercenaries. Mission content varies widely, from attacking targets and sabotage to escort and reconnaissance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can also piece together the state of the world through news reports on mission outcomes and emails from clients.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509800/extras/mission.gif?t=1737777016\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Arena</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the &quot;Arena,&quot; which features 1on1 battles between V3s, tougher opponents await players as they climb the ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The score attack mode is compatible with Steam rankings, allowing players to compete for higher scores in a highly competitive mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509800/extras/arena2.gif?t=1737777016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find your favorite parts and tactics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509800/extras/arena1.gif?t=1737777016\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mercenary Registration","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/44c5f09a697e599106e80b7ea551309c0b5cded5.jpg"},{"name":"Invisible Raid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/e96e8256731ddc35d81ac2b43a21d37fe585fed1.jpg"},{"name":"The One Who Moves","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/6a0194fa8a6e469c7d458b08e604a5432c98d3a1.jpg"},{"name":"Evidence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/69414a9d3b9dcdebddf1ddc600a6fe0a6e7b48e7.jpg"},{"name":"Exposure of Truth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/99591290f49677abc4f0b354680ef69f17b49759.jpg"},{"name":"The Beginning of the End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/78bb830e806e820ddd34ab636f2d503aa42c719e.jpg"},{"name":"Top-notch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/776ab468e518e68e11a3d584a6bd5e0c713c7e2b.jpg"},{"name":"New Face in the Arena","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/7a3e03451e1f094488b99b60ff39a804349d549e.jpg"},{"name":"Top Ranker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/0a4e268971a3e46fed53907d7b9c1e5aed567b10.jpg"},{"name":"The Strongest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2509800/fe12fbc0760d57c5e686d17d34f97e20c28ec2fa.jpg"}],"total":11},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737777016","bac